@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="card shadow-sm p-5">
        <h1 class="display-4 text-primary">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <hr />
        <pre>


        Privacy Policy for Cars Catalog Website
        Last Updated: March 12, 2026

        At Cars Catalog Website, we value your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it,
        and how we protect it.

        1. Information We Collect
        We collect information to provide better services to our users. This includes:

        Personal Information: Name, email address, and contact details provided via our forms.

        Usage Data: Information on how you use our website, including IP addresses and browser types.

        Cookies: Small files stored on your device to improve site navigation and analyze traffic.

        2. How We Use Your Information
        The data we collect is used to:

        Personalize your experience (like showing you cars based on your country selection).

        Improve our website and customer service.

        Send periodic emails regarding your preferences or updates.

        3. Data Protection
        We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. Your data is
        stored behind secured networks and is only accessible by a limited number of persons who have special access 
        rights.

        4. Third-Party Disclosure
        We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personally identifiable information to outside parties unless
        we provide users with advance notice. This does not include website hosting partners and other parties who
        assist us in operating our website.

        5. Your Rights
        You have the right to:

        Request access to the personal data we hold about you.

        Request that we correct or delete your personal information.

        Withdraw consent for data processing at any time.

        6. Contact Us
        If there are any questions regarding this privacy policy, you may contact us using the information below:
        </pre>
    </div>
</div>